snippet.title: Plane Graveyard Simulator - Announcement Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
✈️ Plane Graveyard Simulator is coming to Steam! 🔥 Wishlist Now 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3128610/Plane_Graveyard_Simulator/

Visit the world's largest airplane graveyard and explore the huge desert filled with wrecks. 🛬 Hundreds of tons of steel and rusted electronics are waiting. Dismantle airplanes, earn money from scrap, and complete tasks from your employer! ⚒️

---
